Get the user's Ideal Buyer Profile, purchase-intent tags, and qualification questions. The result is cached on the client. Returns an operator `hint` when no profile is configured yet.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} at the very start of a session to understand what kind of leads the user is looking for.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} per-lead — leadbay_research_lead already includes the per-lead qualification answers (which are scored against these org-level questions).
